r 3V Spannungsversorgung und dem Analog-Pin <code>A0</code> angeschlossen.\nGelangt das Wasser zu den beiden \"Prüfspitzen\", steigt die Spannung an.\nDer gemessene Wert an <code>A0</code> erhöht sich und kann mittels einem Schwellwert in ein digitales Signal umgewandelt werden.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"md-figure-block\"><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading md-figure-image\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 700 843' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-c417db9d9ad9783e20f9fd621d974fbf'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-c417db9d9ad9783e20f9fd621d974fbf)' width='700' height='843' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2b6rcOZQEf1kVxXVxzBuNVqZy%2bFuZDA6BxOISE3Gu%2bP0NqI0ST7YWyUzpDd7yfNXjSohhuF0AidEc0RIZV9HBj6F9pAUtTqQgbkqFhiD0ulu1CaiMwW0rVqCs2AxortIm0kJblm7a9UrSolKvTXFPYm3tuUTprN23flCfj0/Ek5kYkwXkOoWwErUjUcSSRv56EYmzXn7Ycc5sh3LzDwPeae4T9FD/rCYwrf2/bDaBm2INHRZvVKfs9SWjiwVG4wNiPtj6NruALi%2bKA38NYitTUZI9OUMaWfhpD3NSlaf5QGA%2b1RHgrWmuhHJ9FOH5LMOK9IlqCGWklSldBgZQaHOzJBfzFXn3KbRQFdkQX1Miw/MOHVSj7jD/mXIlLgutSKvJek0iP3%2byrskzXx4Uafy07q6kgdcTjPmYJVYmpZcWEsNpAQy2OFDafJIA0AHTF7JgbNj5PXuH%2bleYx1c7fxG31Pl4fa/etWVc5JiyEsyYKJE1gpSy6twpuD%2bZYHiNiOmoOGidnmfKlcpvszrCFHuclKgLaDe/riM017tNTmLQCRYJBHkE6frrh5y9BWInHsVn9BiqtjbGd3Ca6bHDUN3OG4AkXOcA459/VEs81p%2bflSS07GjoAUhfEhlKSLHqB64mkRaEIU86bNoFz6npii5ghvOUGa2Nbtk/bXEqqb6EhEdJu01qv%%2bnrhtjZxmojpU%2bKeoWAKSyhJJ6Dr7Yl%2bW/ldQcm/Mo3bZYbPDDS9wuKUB4mzeytPy318tdMB4zT8ymh5IUJcQh55Sld9DY2sTsL2AA3v6YMkpS%2b4LrW5%2bqUt1iFo2iMOPQ59%2buFRPiHmp%2bW38nYiMR5ajd0oTwkAC9jroPMnEVedKlXJub/c9cbnKvJSJC2nloVKQW3RbUpJ8IO/1xkgtpVIaU6dFHQDB1JTdmZYpBqdeKl92iy6BgT8xVV1AhwadToywrvz1ArtwDdCAbadffGVtNQi55cFSeiuOyGVd%2bOkpSeEW6D6%2b%2bGEVCbBaQarB7NGfulT4krdDd0DhChpYE218vPA/ODCo2ZaJLsQlfMZJIOpKQRuT1xXqLd9M8eCnoLg2tZ43/pHqQwzR48nMVQFnEtlqMi9rp/xe529Ncc7ZnzJMreZ3